", "start": 415.56, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": ">> Right.", "start": 417.6, "duration": 2.24}, {"text": ">> Right, cuz right now I'll bet you have a", "start": 418.56, "duration": 3.64}, {"text": "lot of half-built bridges.", "start": 419.84, "duration": 3.44}, {"text": "Right? And so like we don't need to", "start": 422.2, "duration": 2.96}, {"text": "start building more, we start removing", "start": 423.28, "duration": 3.2}, {"text": "the like everything that's taking all", "start": 425.16, "duration": 3.24}, {"text": "your time so that cuz like now if you", "start": 426.48, "duration": 3.16}, {"text": "had said", "start": 428.4, "duration": 4.32}, {"text": "we're doing $400,000 in profit um and my", "start": 429.64, "duration": 4.48}, {"text": "comp is included in that, I'd be like we", "start": 432.72, "duration": 2.6}, {"text": "probably have some business issues and", "start": 434.12, "duration": 2.6}, {"text": "unfortunately we can't pay anyone else", "start": 435.32, "duration": 3.2}, {"text": "to get in yet cuz it's too thin.", "start": 436.72, "duration": 2.76}, {"text": "So, you got to fix a bunch of other", "start": 438.52, "duration": 2.52}, {"text": "stuff. But given the fact that you got", "start": 439.48, "duration": 3.439}, {"text": "roughly 30% margins from a seller", "start": 441.04, "duration": 3.76}, {"text": "discretionary earning perspective.", "start": 442.919, "duration": 3.121}, {"text": "Um", "start": 444.8, "duration": 3.16}, {"text": "like business is okay. Could you", "start": 446.04, "duration": 3.36}, {"text": "probably improve the sales process?", "start": 447.96, "duration": 3.76}, {"text": "Basically every medical company can.", "start": 449.4, "duration": 5.68}, {"text": "Um so yeah, is it the constraint?", "start": 451.72, "duration": 5.4}, {"text": "Probably not.", "start": 455.08, "duration": 3.839}, {"text": "Cuz if you made an extra $300,000 in", "start": 457.12, "duration": 3.16}, {"text": "profit", "start": 458.919, "duration": 4.481}, {"text": "would that change your life?", "start": 460.28, "duration": 4.48}, {"text": ">> Not really.", "start": 463.4, "duration": 3.24}, {"text": ">> Okay, so the sales so then like the", "start": 464.76, "duration": 3.32}, {"text": "sales isn't the constraint. That might", "start": 466.64, "duration": 3.28}, {"text": "occur if the sales got fixed. The issue", "start": 468.08, "duration": 2.96}, {"text": "is your time.", "start": 469.92, "duration": 1.72}, {"text": ">> Yes.", "start": 471.04, "duration": 3.88}, {"text": ">> Right, so we need to go", "start": 471.64, "duration": 3.28}, {"text": "manpower.", "start": 475.32, "duration": 4.64}, {"text": "Which is the first thing I said.", "start": 476.96, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": ">> [laughter]", "start": 480.12, "duration": 2.02}, {"text": ">> Touché.", "start": 482.36, "duration": 1.64}, {"text": ">> Does that help?", "start": 483.12, "duration": 1.68}, {"text": ">> Yes, thank you.", "start": 484.0, "duration": 3.08}, {"text": ">> You bet.", "start": 484.8, "duration": 2.28}, {"text": "If you are a business owner and you are", "start": 488.92, "duration": 3.52}, {"text": "not growing as fast as you like, I'd", "start": 490.88, "duration": 3.56}, {"text": "like to give you a free gift. So, my", "start": 492.44, "duration": 4.479}, {"text": "team and I put together the $100 scaling", "start": 494.44, "duration": 4.2}, {"text": "road map, which is basically 200 hours", "start": 496.919, "duration": 2.961}, {"text": "of us looking over all the portfolio", "start": 498.64, "duration": 3.68}, {"text": "companies we've had and what stages of", "start": 499.88, "duration": 4.039}, {"text": "growth they went through and more", "start": 502.32, "duration": 3.28}, {"text": "importantly where they got stuck and how", "start": 503.919, "duration": 3.521}, {"text": "they got past it. And so we broke it in", "start": 505.6, "duration": 3.64}, {"text": "these 10 stages and we made this little", "start": 507.44, "duration": 3.36}, {"text": "kind of quiz thing where if you put in", "start": 509.24, "duration": 2.84}, {"text": "your business information, it'll tell", "start": 510.8, "duration": 2.76}, {"text": "you where you're at and the most", "start": 512.08, "duration": 3.28}, {"text": "important part for you, what to do for", "start": 513.56, "duration": 3.039}, {"text": "each of functions of the business across", "start": 515.36, "duration": 2.44}, {"text": "product, marketing, sales, customer", "start": 516.599, "duration": 3.521}, {"text": "success, recruiting, IT, human resources", "start": 517.8, "duration": 4.44}, {"text": "and finance. And so, no matter what", "start": 520.12, "duration": 3.96}, {"text": "you're struggling with, someone else has", "start": 522.24, "duration": 3.8}, {"text": "already struggled with it and solved it.", "start": 524.08, "duration": 3.28}, {"text": "And so I'd like to give you this thing", "start": 526.04, "duration": 2.16}, {"text": "absolutely free. You can go to", "start": 527.36, "duration": 2.479}, {"text": "acquisition.com/roadmap,", "start": 528.2, "duration": 3.2}, {"text": "plug in your business information, and", "start": 529.839, "duration": 3.761}, {"text": "if you want us to actually help you", "start": 531.4, "duration": 3.6}, {"text": "de-constrain the business and you're", "start": 533.6, "duration": 3.04}, {"text": "trying to scale, we'd love to help you", "start": 535.0, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "out. On the thank you page, you can book", "start": 536.64, "duration": 4.16}, {"text": "a call with my team and we will", "start": 538.0, "duration": 4.32}, {"text": "look at the business, see if we can", "start": 540.8, "duration": 2.56}, {"text": "help, and if we can, we'll invite you", "start": 542.32, "duration": 3.04}, {"text": "out to Vegas and we'll do this in person", "start": 543.36, "duration": 4.76}, {"text": "live.", "start": 545.36, "duration": 2.76}]